videos.description: Draymond Green joins Scott Van Pelt to discuss the importance of winning in the NBA, how important it is to Kevin Durant to defeat the Thunder and taking pride in playing hard-nosed defense in the league.

videos.description: Antonio Davis doesn't understand why Thunder players didn't rush onto the court after Zaza Pachulia knocked Russell Westbrook down and stood over him during Wednesday night's Thunder-Warriors game.
